types :
  standard (predefined)
  userdefined
  recursion function(function inside function)
  tail recursion(operation then recursion)
  
  * if arguments are passed then value is taken in function else default value is taken
  higher order function: function as an argument to another function
  
  inline function: inhances functioning of higher order functions
  (it tells compiler to copy parameters and functions to the call site )
inline fun namre(value)

